{
  "stem": "10905.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Back to the train.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then for some reason, we decided not to go to freedom, they send us to a place called Bergen-Belsen in Hannover, Germany.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I don't know how many days that-- that leg of the trip took.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But the train--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Was I frightened then?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was-- I was-- I have to tell you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The only time that I was frightened, I was frightened twice.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Once the day of the bombing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And once when-- and I'll tell you it's something else that happened at [INTERPOSING VOICES] in a little while about what happened.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I was only frightened twice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The first bombing in Belgrade.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Belgrade.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Belgrade.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We arrived at the depot, train depot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was-- being a kid, you know everything is much bigger, much further, much more.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I really don't know how far, but it was quite a distance away from where we were.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We picked up our equipment, luggage, and what have you, and we're just marching and marching.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And primarily on-- as we were coming in, it was primarily on to our left.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Typical barracks, barbed wire, the watch tower.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just-- I don't know how many, but finally we got to a place and that was it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was nobody there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We came in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Again, the barracks, I think were divided alphabetically.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think alphabetically.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And men, one place.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Women with young children in another barrack.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In the men's barracks, there were double decker beds.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In the women's barracks, there were triple decker beds.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't know how many hundreds of people in the hut or barrack.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was one toilet that was functioning, because at night, we were not allowed out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were not allowed.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
